Feature: User shopping cart

  Scenario: Adding items into shopping cart
    Given user is on item page
    When user selects colour/quantity
    And clicks the add to cart option
    Then  item is added to shopping cart

    Scenario: Opening shopping cart
      Given user had added item in shopping cart
      When user hovers over shopping cart icon
      Then sees dropdown
      And clicks on view cart
      Then user should see the added item in shopping cart

